Febraayo 14, 2020, kooxda Feng Zhang waxay sharaxeen borotokoolka isticmaalka farsamada CRISPR-ku saleysan ee SHERLOCK si loo ogaado SARS-CoV-2, oo lagu ogaanayo qaybaha SARS-CoV-2 RNA ee isku dhafan 20 × 10-18 mol/L ilaa 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 nuqul halkiiba microliter ee soo galida) iyadoo la adeegsanayo usha qubeyska wax ka yar hal saac oo aan u baahnayn qalab adag.
