Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa ku dhawaaqay COVID-19 inay tahay masiibo
Arbacadii, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa ku dhawaaqay faafida COVID-19 ee hadda socda - xanuunka uu sababay coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 - inuu yahay masiibo.
Xitaa haddii ereyga "bukaan" uu tixraacayo sida cudurka uu u faafay, ma ahan sida ay u khatar badanyihiin, WHO waxay xustay baahida loo qabo in la booriyo xukuumadaha si ay u talaabsadaan:
Wadamada aduunka dhan weli waxey badali karaan badalida dhacdada.
