Kiiskii ugu horreeyay ee la ogaaday ee coronavirus-ka cusub waxaa la raad raaci karaa 1da Diseembar 2019 ee Wuhan, Hubei, Shiinaha.
Muddo bil gudaheed ah, tirada kiisaska coronavirus ee Hubei ayaa si tartiib tartiib ah u kordhay.
Kiisaska intooda badan waxay la xiriiraan Suuqa Jumlada ee Cunnada Badda ee Huanan, kaas oo sidoo kale iibiya xayawaan nool, hal aragtiina waxay tahay in fayrasku ka yimid mid ka mid ah noocyada xayawaankan; ama, si kale haddii loo dhigo, fayrasku wuxuu leeyahay asal zoonotic ah.
Bishii December 30, koox dhakhaatiir ah oo ka tirsan Isbitaalka Wuhan ayaa u sheegay asxaabtooda inay qabaan "coronavirus SARS la mid ah".
Siddeed ka mid ah dhakhaatiirta, oo uu ku jiro Li Wenliang, ayaa booliisku ku baraarugeen faafinta warar been abuur ah, halka midka kale, Ai Fen, uu madaxda ka waaniyey digniinta uu soo saaray.
Guddiga Caafimaadka ee Wuhan ayaa soo saaray bayaan ay u soo gudbiyeen dadweynaha 31kii Diseembar waxayna ku wargeliyeen WHO.
