Bilowgii iyo badhtamihii Janaayo 2020, fayrasku wuxuu ku faafay gobollada kale ee Shiinaha, oo ay ku xoojisay socdaalka inta lagu gudajiray Sannadka Cusub ee Shiinaha iyo sababta oo ah Wuhan waa xarun gaadiid iyo meel weyn oo tareen ah.
Janaayo 20, Shiinaha ayaa soo warisay ku dhawaad 140 xaaladood oo cusub maalin gudaheed, oo ay ku jiraan laba qof oo ku sugan Beijing iyo qof ku sugan Shenzhen.
