WHO waxay ammaantay dadaalka dawlada Shiinaha ay ugu jirto maamulida iyo xakamaynta cudurka.
WHO waxay ogaatay farqiga u dhexeeya dillaaca SARS ee 2002-2004 markii mas'uuliyiinta Shiinaha lagu eedeeyay inay daboolayaan oo ay ka hortagaan dadaallada ka hortagga iyo xakamaynta iyo dhibaatada hadda jirta ee ay dowladda dhexe "si joogto ah u cusbooneysiiso si looga fogaado argagaxa ka hor fasaxa Sannadka Cusub".
Bishii Janaayo 23, markii ay ka soo jawaabtay go'aanka dowladda dhexe ee ku saabsan in la xakameeyo gaadiidka Wuhan, wakiilka WHO Gauden Galea wuxuu sheegay in inkasta oo tallaabada "si cad aysan u ahayn talo soo jeedin WHO ah", haddana waxay u ahayd "tilmaam aad u muhiim ah oo ku saabsan ballanqaadkeenna in la joojiyo cudurka meesha uu ku badan yahay" wuxuuna ku tilmaamay "mid aan hore u dhicin taariikhda caafimaadka dadweynaha". Bishii Janaayo 30, ka dib markii la xaqiijiyay in dadku ay ku wareejiyeen dadka ka baxsan Shiinaha iyo kororka kiisaska dalal kale, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday cudurka inuu yahay Xaalad Caafimaad Bulsho oo Caalamiga ah (PHEIC), tallaabada 6aad ee PHEIC tan iyo markii ugu horreysay la soo saaray cudurka hargabka ee 2009.
Agaasimaha guud ee WHO Tedros Adhanom ayaa sheegay in PHEIC loo soo saaray "halista faafitaanka caalamiga ah, gaar ahaan dalalka dakhligoodu hooseeyo ama kuwa dhexe oo aan lahayn nidaam caafimaad oo wanaagsan.
Jawaabta ku aaddan hirgelinta xaddidaadaha safarka, Tedros wuxuu ku caddeeyay in "aysan jirin wax sabab ah oo lagu soo rogo tallaabooyin si aan loo baahnayn u carqaladeeya safarka iyo ganacsiga caalamiga ah" iyo "WHO ma talinayso xaddidaadda ganacsiga iyo dhaqdhaqaaqa".
