b'Enzyme angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku dheggan dusha sare ee unugyada (halbeegga unugyada) ee sambabada, wadnaha, wadnaha, kelyaha, iyo mindhicirada.
ACE2 waxay leedahay waxqabad ka soo horjeeda enzyme-ka beddelashada angiotensin (ACE), iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa tirada angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadida Angiotensin (1-7), taas oo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed daawo oo rajo leh oo lagu daaweynayo cudurada wadnaha. ACE2 sidoo kale waxay u adeegtaa sidii barta gelitaanka unugyada ee qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
ACE2 nooca aadanaha waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan 'HaaCE2'.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 waa zinc-ku jira metaloenzyme ku yaala unugyada unugyada unugyada iyo unugyada kale.
ACE2 wuxuu leeyahay N-terminal M2 domain peptidase iyo C-terminal renal collectrin amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa borotiin nooc I ah oo ah unugyo unugyo unugyo ah, oo leh unugyo enzymatically firfircoon oo ku jira unugyada unugyada unugyada iyo unugyada unugyada.
ACE2 domain-ka dibadda waxaa laga soocaa domain-ka transmembrane-ka, oo loo yaqaan sheddase, iyo borotiinka la kala saaray oo la soo saaray ayaa loo sii daayaa dhiigga, ugu dambayntiina waxaa lagu sii daayaa kaadida.
ACE2 wuxuu ku jiraa xubnaha badankood: ACE2 wuxuu ku dhegan yahay xuubka unugyada gaar ahaan unugyada alveolar-ka ee sanbabada nooca II, enterocytes-ka mindhicirka yar, unugyada endothelium ee arteries iyo xididdada, iyo unugyada muruqyada caadiga ah ee arterial ee xubnaha badankood.
Ereyada mRNA ee ACE2 waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa maskaxda, maskaxda, hypothalamus, iyo maskaxda.
Waxan ku jirnaa ACE2 oo ah isku dheelitirka ACE.
ACE wuxuu u shaqeeyaa si uu u sameeyo angiotensin I.
Ugu dambeyntii, ACE2 waxay ka gooysaa karboksil-dhamaadka amino acid phenylalanine ee angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) waxayna hydrolyse u sameysaa angiotensin (1-7) vasodilator (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale jaban kartaa tiro kale oo peptides ah oo ay ku jiraan [des-Arg9] -bradikinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorfin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa taraafikada xuubka ee dhexdhexaadka ah ee SLC6A19 waxayna ku lug leedahay cudurka Hartnup.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 wuxuu u adeegaa sida barta ugu weyn ee gelitaanka unugyada unugyada loo yaqaan 'coronaviruses', oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus-ka sababa SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus-ka keena COVID-19).
Si gaar ah, isku xirida borotiinka S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada ee leh ACE2 enzymatic domain waxay keentaa endositosis iyo wareejinta fayraska iyo enzymes ee ku yaal unugyada gudahooda.
Gelitaanka fayrasku wuxuu kaloo u baahan yahay protein S priming by TMPRSS2 protease host serine, xannibaadda taas oo hadda la baaray sidii daaweyn suurtagal ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, bulshooyinka xirfadleyda iyo hay'adaha sharciyeeyda badankood waxay ku talinayaan in la sii wado daaweynta ACE-da iyo ARB-yada.
Dib-u-eegis nidaamsan iyo falanqeyn, oo la daabacay 11 Luulyo 2012, ayaa lagu ogaaday in "isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ay keeneen hoos u dhac weyn oo ah 34% ee halista cudurka sambabada marka loo eego koontaroolka".
Intaa waxaa dheer, "Isticmaalka ACE inhibitors sidoo kale waxay hoos u dhigeysaa halista sambabada ee bukaanka oo leh khatar sare oo ah sambabada, gaar ahaan bukaanka qaba istaroogga iyo wadnaha oo aan shaqeyn.
Isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ayaa sidoo kale lala xiriiriyay dhimashada oo la xiriirta oofsiga, in kasta oo natiijooyinku ay ahaayeen kuwo ka yar xoog marka loo eego khatarta guud ee sambabada".
Isku-darka ACE2 ee bini'aadamka (rhACE2) waxaa la filayaa inuu noqdo daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay dhaawaca sambabada ee daran, waxayna u muuqataa inay kordhiso hemodynamicka sambabada iyo oksijiinta oksijiinta ee doofaarka leh cudurka neefsashada ee lipoplisakarid-ka.
Nolosha nuska ah ee rhACE2 ee aadanaha waa 10 saacadood oo leh 30 daqiiqo oo shaqo ah marka lagu daro 24 saacadood oo dherer ah.
